Windows (PowerShell):
powershell

git clone https://github.com/shaman2025/yoka_exiftool.git; cd yoka_exiftool; pip install -r requirements.txt; python yoka_exiftool.py

Linux/macOS:
bash

git clone https://github.com/shaman2025/yoka_exiftool.git && cd yoka_exiftool && pip install -r requirements.txt && python yoka_exiftool.py
